<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><a style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi&nbsp;</span></a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">{!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Following your recent Kingsbridge policy purchase, we have received notification from your bank that the payment has been unsuccessful.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">We have already tried to call you to discuss this and will again in the next few working days.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Unfortunately, if we are unable to speak with you and collect payment</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, in accordance with the terms and conditions,&nbsp;</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your policy will be cancelled from inception.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">This means the policy will be null and void and you will have no rights to any cover under this policy at any time.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Alternatively, please contact us at your earliest convenience on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;to discuss this further.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
